尼克·卡特“仍在处理”他弟弟亚伦的死https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carter-still-processing-the-death-of-his-brother-aaron-3531509?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=nick-carter-still-processing-他的兄弟亚伦之死Surej SinghMon, 06 Nov 2023 03:42:41 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3531509 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他还表示，他无法再与弟弟“和解”，这让他“受伤”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carter-still-processing-the-death-of-his-brother-aaron-3531509">尼克·卡特“仍在处理”他弟弟亚伦去世的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nick-aaron-carter@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-carter">亚伦卡特</a>英年早逝一年后，他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-carter">哥哥尼克</a>说他仍然无法处理这种情况。</p><p>跟<a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1389195/how-nick-carter-is-healing-one-year-after-brother-aaron-carters-death" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>E说话！新闻报道中</em></a>，两人中年龄较大的尼克、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/backstreet-boys">后街男孩</a>​​明星尼克表示，去年 11 月 5 日亚伦的去世“仍然令人难以置信”。尼克继续说道：“我仍在处理整个情况并试图理解它——因为事实并非如此。但我希望有一天我能明白这一切。”</p><p>去年11月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaron-carter-has-been-found-dead-at-his-home-aged-34-3343362">，这位流行艺术家被发现躺在加利福尼亚州兰卡斯特家中的浴缸里失去知觉</a>，医护人员赶到现场后被宣布死亡。他当时 34 岁。</p><p>尼克还告诉<em>E！</em>亚伦去世的<em>消息</em>更具毁灭性，因为这意味着兄弟俩的紧张关系无法修复。 “无论他和我在生活中经历了什么，我们总是能够弥补，总是能够回到那个地方——但现在我不能了，这很痛苦，”尼克说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3343652" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3343652" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3343652" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/aaron-nick-carter-2004-getty.jpg" alt="卡特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/aaron-nick-carter-2004-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/aaron-nick-carter-2004-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/aaron-nick-carter-2004-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/aaron-nick-carter-2004-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/aaron-nick-carter-2004-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/aaron-nick-carter-2004-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3343652" class="wp-caption-text">尼克和亚伦·卡特，2004 年。图片来源：Jeff Kravitz/FilmMagic, Inc.</figcaption></figure><p>上个月末，卡特一家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaron-carters-family-to-sue-doctors-and-pharmacies-over-his-death-3525071">提起过失死亡诉讼，声称医生和药剂师对亚伦的死亡负有部分责任</a>。在诉讼中，据称鉴于卡特的病史，医生和沃尔格林药房不应该给他开阿片类药物。它还声称，错误的处方和配药影响了卡特的判断力和心理健康，导致了他的死亡。</p><p>卡特去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carter-pays-tribute-to-late-brother-aaron-addiction-and-mental-illness-is-the-real-villain-3343650">他的兄弟尼克·卡特在网上悼念</a>。 “我的心碎了，”他写道。 “尽管我和哥哥的关系很复杂，但我对他的爱从未消退。我一直抱有希望，希望有一天他能走上一条健康的道路，并最终找到他迫切需要的帮助。”</p><p>尼克补充道：“我会比任何人都更想念我的兄弟。我爱你奇兹。现在你终于可以享受在地球上永远找不到的平静了……我爱你，宝贝弟弟。” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carter-launches-childrens-mental-health-fund-in-wake-of-brother-aarons-death-3348998">在卡特去世后，这位后街男孩明星还设立了一个儿童心理健康基金</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-carter-still-processing-the-death-of-his-brother-aaron-3531509">尼克·卡特“仍在处理”他弟弟亚伦去世的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
