g 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <i>《好汉两个半》</i>主创查克·洛尔透露，他已经“治愈”了与该剧前明星查理·辛的关系。</p><p>这一消息是在洛尔创作、辛主演的一部新喜剧电视连续剧<em>《如何成为赌徒》</em>推出之前发布的。</p><p> 2011年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/charlie-sheen-fired-from-two-and-a-half-men-582223">辛因行为变得越来越不稳定而被<em>《好汉两个半》</em>解雇</a>。最终导致洛尔和辛之间的关系公开破裂，后者将洛尔描述为“小丑”和“一个愚蠢、愚蠢的人”，并发表了一些反犹太诽谤。 </p><figure id="attachment_3531231" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3531231" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3531231" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/two_half_men_awards.jpg" alt="好汉两个半演员表" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/two_half_men_awards.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/two_half_men_awards-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/two_half_men_awards-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/two_half_men_awards-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/two_half_men_awards-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/two_half_men_awards-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3531231" class="wp-caption-text">查理·辛 (Charlie Sheen) 与《好汉两个半》的演员们在 2004 年人民选择奖颁奖典礼上（摄影：Jeff Kravitz/FilmMagic）</figcaption></figure><p>辛因在<em>《野战排》</em>和<em>《华尔街》</em>中的角色而声名鹊起，是当时电视上片酬最高的演员，但他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/ashton-kutcher-to-replace-charlie-sheen-in-two-and-873772">在剧中被阿什顿·库彻取代</a>。</p><p>然而，随着洛尔和联合创始人尼克·巴凯为<em>《如何成为赌徒》</em>寻找男主角，洛尔在接受<a href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/two-and-a-half-men-chuck-lorre-charlie-sheen-make-amends-1235776341/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Variety</i></a>采访时透露，他认为辛非常适合这个新角色，并向他提出了报价。</p><p> “我很紧张，但几乎我们一开始交谈，我就想起我们曾经是朋友，”洛尔分享道。 “那种友谊似乎突然又出现了。”</p><p> “我不想对此表现得太伤感，但它很治愈。而且他也完全是为了取笑自己。当他走到桌边读到那一集时，我走上前，我们拥抱了。真是太棒了。”</p><p> <i>《好汉两个半》</i>从 2003 年到 2015 年总共播出了 12 季。在回忆与辛的成功时，洛尔说道：“在全部崩溃之前，我们一起制作了 170 集。很多时候，我们都玩得很开心。”</p><p>他接着澄清说，尽管他们过去存在裂痕，但他和辛之间的关系在 2023 年会变得更好。“假设他处于一个好的位置，我也会处于一个好的位置，”他说。</p><p> 2021 年，辛在接受<a href="https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/charlie-sheen-interview-tiger-blood-winning-internet-two-and-a-half-men-regrets-160054347.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>雅虎</i></a>采访时反思了他与洛尔的公开不和。 <a href="https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/charlie-sheen-interview-tiger-blood-winning-internet-two-and-a-half-men-regrets-160054347.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>娱乐</i></a>。</p><p> “我有 55 种不同的方法来处理这种情况，但我选择了 56 种，”他说。 “所以，你知道，我认为我在崩溃后的成长，或者向前融化，或者在某个地方融化——无论你想给它贴上什么标签——它必须从我在这一切中的角色的绝对所有权开始。真是太年轻了。”</p><p> <i>《如何成为赌徒》</i>将于 11 月 30 日在美国 HBO Max 首播。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/charlie-sheen-heals-relationship-with-two-and-a-half-men-creator-3531230">查理·辛“治愈”与《好汉两个半》创作者关系的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
可怕海峡拒绝“巨额资金”进行改革https://www.nme.com/news/music/dire-straits-turn-down-huge-amounts-of-money-to-reform-3531223?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=dire-straits-turn-down-巨额资金改革Max PilleySun, 05 Nov 2023 16:44:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3531223 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="恐怖海峡" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我希望人们停止向我提供巨额资金来恢复[恐怖海峡]”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dire-straits-turn-down-huge-amounts-of-money-to-reform-3531223">《可怕海峡》拒绝“巨额资金”进行改革</a>后的消息首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="恐怖海峡" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_knopfler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dire-straits">Dire Straits 的</a>一位创始成员透露，近年来，Dire Straits 拒绝了“巨额资金”来改革乐队。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/interviews/dire-straits-john-illsley-interview-mark-knopfler/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《电讯报》</i></a>采访时，80 年代摇滚巨头中常驻的贝斯手约翰·伊尔斯利 (John Illsley) 证实，乐队继续收到重聚的重要财务报价，但他也暗示他们仍然不感兴趣。</p><p>谈到最近他与乐队前任经理保罗·克罗克福德 (Paul Crockford) 的会面时，伊尔斯利说：“每次我们吃午饭时，他都会对我说，‘我希望人们停止向我提供巨额资金来投入 [Dire Straits]”。重新走到一起。&#39;” </p><figure id="attachment_3531226" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3531226" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3531226" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_live_aid.jpg" alt="与斯汀 (Sting) 一起参与“恐怖海峡” (Live Aid) 活动" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_live_aid.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_live_aid-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_live_aid-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_live_aid-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_live_aid-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dire_straits_live_aid-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3531226" class="wp-caption-text"> 1985 年，Dire Straits 与 Sting 一起在 Live Aid 表演（摄影：FG/Bauer-Griffin/Getty Images）170612F1</figcaption></figure><p> Dire Straits 于 1988 年短暂解散两年，并于 1995 年永久解散，共发行了六张录音室专辑。</p><p>伊尔斯利现在反映，当乐队的演出结束时，他“非常高兴”，回忆起当他们最终解散时，他感到“精神上、身体上和情感上都疲惫不堪”。</p><p> “我们大多数的婚姻都在破裂，我们很少见到我们的孩子——这都是错误的。这是乐队成员身上经常发生的事情，”他继续说道。</p><p> Dire Straits 赢得了四项格莱美奖和三项全英音乐奖，他们 1985 年的专辑《Brothers in Arms》是英国有史以来第八畅销专辑。他们在全球销售了超过 1 亿张唱片，并于 2018 年入选摇滚名人堂。</p><p> 2008年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dire-straits-3-1332995">伊尔斯利透露，他曾与可怕海峡主唱马克·诺普弗勒（Mark Knopfler）接触</a>，讨论重组乐队的可能性，但遭到拒绝。</p><p> “我认为我们肯定还剩下一场巡演，可能还有另一张唱片，”伊尔斯利当时说道。 “但他 [Knopfler] 现在正在创作不同类型的音乐。作为一名独奏艺术家，他的表现非常出色，所以向他致敬。他正在做他正在做的事情，度过了一段非常愉快的时光。”</p><p> Illsley has reflected that the absence of the band has left a “massive vacuum” in his life, but he appreciates that it has allowed him to explore other creative directions. “I was in London studying painting, I got some lessons, made a terrible mess for seven or eight years, and then started doing art shows. I thought, &#39;OK, this is fun&#39;. And I stopped playing music for quite a while. I leant the bass against the wall and said &#39;Thank you very much but I&#39;m doing something different now&#39;.”</p><p> On August 31, Jack Sonni, who played guitar in Dire Straits between 1984 and 1988, including on &#39;Brothers in Arms&#39;, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dire-straits-guitarist-jack-sonni-has-died-3492079">died at the age of 68</a> .</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dire-straits">Mark Knopfler</a> continues to record solo material and is known for his work on film scores, including Local Hero (1983), The Princess Bride (1987) and Wag the Dog (1998).</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dire-straits-turn-down-huge-amounts-of-money-to-reform-3531223">Dire Straits turn down “huge amounts of money” to reform</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
